### steps to install promethuis.

https://prometheus.io/
click on down and copy the prometheus for linyx
Go to CLI and enter wget <the link you copied>
once done, extract the tar file using tar -xvf 
Go inside it and edit the promatheos yaml file and enter the worker node details.



Do the same in the worker node, but but the file is node exporter.


execute the shell and make sure to enable the port on master 9090 and in worker 9100

Open the dashbord using ip and the port.
Make sure it is UP in the target.
